  11,104,A t NeswexxeĂŽ kan ar lajel iuran
  11,105,"Ass ideg ara d ias, ur d ipmeslay yiwen, siwa ma s tesriĂȘ iS. Ad ilin igeswaĂȘen, isaĂądiyen"
